<bodytext searchtype="COMMENTARY">
<p>
<text>See 
<remotelink dpsi="05CC" refpt="UCPN.LC.S16-5" remotekey1="REFPTID" service="DOC-ID">[LCA07 s 16.5]</remotelink>
 &#x201c;Validity of appointment of &#x2018;Acting Judicial Officers&#x2019;.&#x201d;</text></p>
</bodytext>
</level></leg:comntry>
